N2  - The purpose of this paper is to discuss a number of functional equations which arise in the ?optimal inventory? problem. This is a particular case of the general problem of ordering in the face of an uncertain future demand. Actually, an important aspect of the problem is that of determining a suitable criterion of cost, one which is both realistic and analytically malleable.
